org.csapi.csapicore.core
Class Report

java.lang.Object
  org.csapi.csapicore.core.Report

public class Report
extends java.lang.Object

This class features a set of Change Synergy records, along with informations relative to the report: attribute list and query string. All records in this class must have at least the attributes specified in the attributes String[]. The Report class is responsible for checking records attributes when entered.

Author:
Boris Baldassari

toStrings

public java.lang.String[] toStrings()
Returns an array of String representing the report. Each element of the array is a toString representation of a record. The Vector implementation allows to keep the sorting order of records used when building the report.
